avoid political heat by adopting an environmental platform that harmonizes enviromental goals with increasing education and prosperity.

<li>New Heritage analysis: "As <a href="/heritage/library/categories/forpol/fyi122.html">Yeltsin's Health Fades</a>, the Succession Struggle Intensifies in Russia"

