<DOCNO>WT16-B03-16</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000237-B009-370</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/heritage/commentary/opbj3.html 204.71.237.86 19970108030205 text/html 7557
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 03:02:22 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 16-Dec-96 19:18:12 GMT
