<center><h3>Current Events &amp; Issues</h3>
<h4>(Updated 1/7/97)</h4></center>
<ul>

<p><li>There is a double standard in Washington when it comes to 
ethics. Find out why in today's 
<a href="/townhall/FRC/radio/c97a07.html">radio commentary</a>.

<p><li>William Shakespeare and other great authors of English 
literature are no longer required reading at most of the nation's 
top colleges and universities! Find out more about it in this 
week's issue of <a href="/townhall/FRC/edfacts/edfacts.html"><i>Ed 
Facts</i></a>.

