<title>Outside The Beltway -- Arizona</title>
<body  bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">

<center>
<img src="/townhall/columnists/otb/otb.gif">
</center>
<br>

<img align="left" alt="Arizona State Flag" hspace=15 vspace=25 src="/townhall/columnists/otb/arizonac.gif">
<br>
<br>

<h1>
Arizona Contributors
</h1>

<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<a href="mailto:MLGedit@aol.com"><b>Mark L. Genrich</a>, The Phoenix Gazette</b>
<br>
<ul>
<li><a href="AZ/genrich2.html">The Lights Went Out... Again</a>
<li> <a href="/townhall/columnists/otb/AZ/genrich1.html">President Clinton And Missile Defense</a>
</ul>

