http://www.sbsc.org:80/townhall/columnists/otb/MI/acton1.html 204.71.237.86 19970108032601 text/html 6135
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 03:26:18 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 13-Aug-96 16:06:14 GMT
Content-length: 5948
