http://www.sbsc.org:80/townhall/columnists/otb/NY/freed1.html 204.71.237.86 19970108032711 text/html 6214
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 03:27:27 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 21:18:30 GMT
