<TITLE>The American POW/MIA Experience</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2>"The American POW/MIA Experience:<BR>History, Testimony, and Artistic Representation"</FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=+2>The S. Dillon Ripley Center (Room 3111)<BR> of The Woodrow Wilson Center for Scholars<BR>
(Smithsonian Castle)</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><B>NOVEMBER 8, 1996</B></CENTER>
<P>
<B>CONTACT:<BR>
Dr. Peter Rollins<BR>
Rt.3, Box 80<BR>
Cleveland, OK 74020<BR>
<a href="mailto:Rollins@osuunx.ucc.okstate.edu">Rollins@osuunx.ucc.okstate.edu</a><BR>
(918) 243-7637 and fax 5995</B>
<P>
<B>Alternative contact:<BR>
Rudi Gresham, Executive Director<BR>
Vietnam Veterans Institute<BR>
1003 Blue Springs Rd.<BR>
Orange City, FL 32763<BR>
V: (904) 228-0793 and fax (904) 775-9917</B>
