http://www.sbsc.org:80/townhall/columnists/otb/WA/malkin4.html 204.71.237.86 19970108032841 text/html 6533
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 03:28:58 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 03-Sep-96 18:11:24 GMT
