<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/abic/gopwoman.html.cgi 204.71.237.86 19970108033646 text/html 7646
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 03:37:01 GMT
